=head1 NAME

FLAT_FIELD - flat field the SCUBA array

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Flat field the SCUBA array.

=head1 TASKS

Uses the SURF FLATFIELD task.

=cut


# Find input and output name
($in, $out) = $Frm->inout("_flat");

# Run the task
$Mon{surf_mon}->obeyw("flatfield", "in=$in out=$out");

# Update file
$Frm->file($out);

print colored ("ORAC says: Flatfielded data written to $out\n",'magenta');
